item.title: about
item.description: But enough about me, thank you for taking the time to check out my website! This is a place where I try to put all (or at least some) of my completed projects so that other people can see them. I also try to write a little bit on the blog here, though I can’t make any promises about the consistency of quality from post to post. What I’m interested in writing about varies wildly from month to month, so there is very little cohesion in theme.
